CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1957, pg. 16 reads: "6. The A & P Food Stores booth dispensed coffee to thousands each night. Attendants, Mrs. Dolores Redwood and Mrs. Frances Nunn are shown with representatives, Earl Hughey and Charles Muehlman"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait including Dolores Redwood, Frances Nunn, Earl Hughey, and Charles Muehlman, posed at A&P Food Stores booth at the 1957 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair in the Syria Mosque
